        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/31563144/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/31563144/" class="">第79页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/annelike/" class=" " title="竹嬾">竹嬾</a>
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="31563144">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <div class="ll">
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/31563144/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/small/public/p31563144-1.jpg"></a>
                  </div>
                  <span class=""> 


一切事物的现象---甚至石头和盔甲的现象-----同样也是一张表皮、一张薄膜。温暖的、冰冷的、皱巴巴的、鲜嫩的、干燥的、湿润的、柔软的、坚硬的、粗糙的，可见世界的薄膜覆盖着我们睁开眼睛所能见到的一切东西。它欺骗我们，如同斗篷欺骗公牛。

 </span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2014-05-11 19:52</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">1人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p31563144-1.jpg" alt="The Maja undressed"><br><span class="pic-title">The Maja undressed</span></div><div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div><blockquote><q>一切事物的现象---甚至石头和盔甲的现象-----同样也是一张表皮、一张薄膜。温暖的、冰冷的、皱巴巴的、鲜嫩的、干燥的、湿润的、柔软的、坚硬的、粗糙的，可见世界的薄膜覆盖着我们睁开眼睛所能见到的一切东西。它欺骗我们，如同斗篷欺骗公牛。</q></blockquote><div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div><div class="middle"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p31563144-2.jpg" alt="The Maja Dressed"><br><span class="pic-title">The Maja Dressed</span></div>
